TY  - JOUR
T1  - Credibility of Confidence Sets in Nonstandard Econometric Problems
AU  - Müller, Ulrich K.
AU  - Norets, Andriy
Y1  - 2016/11/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA14023
